=====================
bethisad.talideon.com
=====================

This repo contains an Ansible deployment playbook for the site
bethisad.talideon.com, which is a
`River of News <http://scripting.com/2014/06/02/whatIsARiverOfNewsAggregator.html>`_
style aggregator for the `Ill Bethisad <http://ib.frath.net/w/Main_Page>`_
alternate history community.

It's powered by the `Planet Venus <https://github.com/rubys/venus>`_
aggregator.

If you wish to be included in the aggregator, consider making a pull request
to modifying `templates/config.ini.j2`, adding a section with the URL and name
of your site.

